{"tid":2146951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲呢篇野點駁好？","createTime":"2020-08-09T02:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T03:15:16.000Z","uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"01061a1b2572d02188af5a917dd05fb4471b0f76","tid":2146951,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"陳雲：歐洲多國流行病學家及衛生高官指出，口罩無助防疫。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭醫護部長塔瑪拉&middot;範方舟說：「從醫療角度來看, 沒有證據表明戴著口罩會產生醫療效果，所以我們決定不強加國家義務。」<br />\n<br />\n國家公共衛生和環境研究所發言人Coen Berends說：「&prime;根據當前的證據，公共場所的口罩不需要, 沒有好處, 甚至可能會有負面影響。」<br />\n<br />\n瑞典頂級傳染病專家Anders Tegnell說：「隨著瑞典感染的人數迅速減少，我們認為在瑞典戴著口罩沒有意義，甚至在公共交通上也沒有甚麼意義。」"},{"pid":"0ce69543dcd22d52cc300b434c8d99746fbd80dd","tid":2146951,"uid":41873,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:30:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">政權維穩打手一隻</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6FxdjS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6FxdjS.png&h=37f8516e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce36ce5cec4f24926d68112f5e9878aeaab8d220","tid":2146951,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"0ce69543dcd22d52cc300b434c8d99746fbd80dd","tid":2146951,"uid":41873,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:30:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">政權維穩打手一隻</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6FxdjS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6FxdjS.png&h=37f8516e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"人哋係燒山fans 啫，未有耐去到維穩打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a89df37e521ad74bc17a2e25eae2eb852f4ecf","tid":2146951,"uid":219156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ce36ce5cec4f24926d68112f5e9878aeaab8d220","tid":2146951,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"0ce69543dcd22d